snippet.title: Citytopia Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Citytopia, an exciting city builder and management game with beautiful 3D graphics and an innovative needs-based contract system.  Open card packs to build and upgrade all aspects of the city, from buildings to vehicles to the roads themselves. Master the supply chain to transform your city into a thriving metropolis!

Follow us:  
Facebook: http://bit.ly/2HolG8a
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Citytopiagame
Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/citytopiagame/
